Economy Outlook
Top sectors: finance(fintech), technology, and logistics.
Labor Market
Over 480,000 employees in Q3 2023, with 226,000 cross-border workers, mainly from France, Belgium, and Germany.
Workforce Composition
Approximately 75% consists of immigrant workers or cross-border commuters
